Just a note to Allison: I appreciate your rating and comments, but please understand that the comments without ratings are just that, comments. They do not "skew" the ratings. They may, however, help cooks, when their questions are answered. I find that often there are responses entered (primarily "no, I would not make this again") without any rating or comments. This accounts for the low % compared with the comments. For those who helpfully respond to other cooks, keep it up!

